kpi.name: M387B2C4

kpi_info.title: Mean time of unsuccessful call setup (MSC)
kpi_info.use: Mean time of unsuccessful call setup service attempts in seconds in ASCII reports and in 10 ms in XML reports. Mean time is calculated by dividing the value of the unsuccessful total call setup service time reservation by the value of unsuccessful call setup service attempts.

kpi.kpi_alias: Mean time of unsuccessful call setup (MSC)
